title: Employ the services of VaynerNFT for public relations and marketing counseling.
body:
"If we seriously/consistently invest a % of our DAO’s income to hire their support to get us more exposure, adding it to our budget, it’s a no brainer that we’ll soon become one of Gary Vee’s favourite projects to be promoted and mentioned on his multiple platforms to the millions and millions of investors, influencers and entertainment/tech celebrities who follow him. He’s the one who initially brought mainstream attention and A list celebrity endorsements to Punks." 
Do you approve the usage of DAO funds to hire VaynerNFT for PR/Marketing counseling services?
author: 0xa11435b21e0Eff08A6c2c5b8316ACC94054e8bAB
